title: I Wonder If Columbus Did This Workout | Mr. Fit | with Mark A. Cinelli
text:
Warm Up for 5-7 minutes
Stretch for 5 minutes
Prep: Perform 1 round of 15 reps for the following ex's
C = Curls
O = Overhead Shoulder Press
L = Lunges
U = Up Up Down Down Plank
M = Medball Slam
B = Body Weight Squat
U = Up Up Down Down Plank
S = Sit Ups
D = Decline Push Ups
A = Ab Rollouts
Y = "Y" Shoulder Raise
REST - 1 min
The Nina = 3 Rounds of 5 push ups and 10 BB Rows
The Pinta = 2 Rounds of 10 Rev Lunges and 20 mountain climbers each
The Santa Maria = 1 Round of 500 meter row and 300 yard shuttle run
REST - 2 min
"1492 Workout". Perform the following
1 mile Run
Then 4 Rounds of 9 burpees and 9 squats
finish with 1 mile run
Stay Active, Stay Fit!
